  "html": "<h2 class=\"\" id=\"2025-06\">2025-06</h2>\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"daily-check-in--reflections\">Daily Check-In &#x26; Reflections</h3>\n<!-- Note any physical activity, mindfulness practice, or self-care -->\n<ul class=\"list-disc\">\n<li class=\"\">Thu 4<div class=\"\"></div> PM: To extract lat/lng from exif from a photo with exiftool: exiftool -GPSPosition -n ~/Desktop/IMG_8834.HEIC</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"\" id=\"-learning--media\">📚 Learning &#x26; Media</h3>\n<!-- Books, articles, movies, TV shows, podcasts consumed -->\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"LM Studio downloading multiple large language models while displaying tagging instructions for categorizing ontological debt content.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1738605176/Screenshot_2025-02-03_at_12.52.41_PM.png\" alt=\"LM Studio downloading multiple large language models while displaying tagging instructions for categorizing ontological debt content.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1738605176/Screenshot_2025-02-03_at_12.52.41_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1738605176/Screenshot_2025-02-03_at_12.52.41_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1738605176/Screenshot_2025-02-03_at_12.52.41_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1738605176/Screenshot_2025-02-03_at_12.52.41_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"LM Studio downloading multiple large language models while displaying tagging instructions for categorizing ontological debt content.\" width=\"2874\" height=\"2474\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.74deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2874×2474\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"